abstract: The National Football League said yesterday that a review of films was inconclusive as to whether Walter Payton, the Bears' running star, fumbled at a critical point of Chicago's loss at Atlanta last Sunday.

UNIVERSITY PARK, Pa., Nov. 28-- Pittsburgh kept alive its slim chances of winning the mythical national collegiate football championship today by scoring a 14-9 victory over Penn State in a superb defensive struggle on cold, soggy turf.

abstract: PORT WASHINGTON, L.I., Nov. 27 (AP)--Craig Virgin, the holder of the American record for 10,000 meters and the world cross country champion, captured the Port Washington five-mile run today in 23 minutes 27.4 seconds.
